# ğŸ´ Shadow SDK - Sovereign Shadow Internal Toolbox

**The unified Python SDK powering the Sovereign Shadow Trading Empire**

## ğŸ¯ What is Shadow SDK?

Shadow SDK is the internal developer toolkit that powers all components of the Sovereign Shadow Trading Empire. It provides a consistent, pythonic interface to the Four-Layer Shadow Scanner Architecture:

- **ShadowScope**: Market scanner core (real-time intelligence)
- **ShadowPulse**: Live signal streaming & heartbeat monitoring
- **ShadowSnaps**: Snapshot & historical analytics
- **ShadowSynapse**: AI reasoning & orchestration layer

## ğŸ“¦ Installation

### From Source (Recommended for Development)
